title: (Tues Early Bird) Top 5 Rejected Segments! + The Bobby Bones Show Recommends + Celeb Net Worth Game
itunes:title: (Tues Early Bird) Top 5 Rejected Segments! + The Bobby Bones Show Recommends + Celeb Net Worth Game
description:
Bobby shares the Top 5 rejected segments from the last month. These are all ideas that didn’t make the air because they were so bad or would get us in trouble. The show shares products and services they use in their personal life that they want to recommend to you! The cast tries to guess which celeb has the higher net worth…it’s a lot harder than you think!
